metadata.name: Morning Lessons, 2022
metadata.description:
Morning Lessons, 2022 is a 4K looping video that is 1/1, and is part of The Ethereal Dispatch Collection by Odell Hussey.

It features a morning scene with two monks observing the passing clouds and rising sun in a surreal land. It's the beginning of something amazing!

It's inspired by my life long pursuit of spiritual connection. I've always had a fascination with the ways in which humanity connects with it's spiritual side. This collection and piece touch on that focus.
